{"tid":1876248,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"起訴醫護前 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2020-02-12T09:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T09:49:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd208d114da3047a4440006cb5f6d18aa85b0a4","tid":1876248,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200212/20860561/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200212%2F20860561%2F&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GPcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=b3a56166\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200212%2F20860561%2F&h=2970b012\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200212/20860561/</a><br />\n<br />\n起訴醫護前 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200212/large/1581414409_3fd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200212%2Flarge%2F1581414409_3fd6.jpg&h=0c0acd35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姐姐葉劉高調表態，任何病人如果在醫護罷工期間，醫療服務受影響，歡迎向她們黨團求助，他們提供法律支援，向罷工醫護提出民事索償。<br />\n<br />\n好提議，老人家不能覆診的確人命攸關，葉劉的確周到。但等等，可否一次過，為病人提供其他起訴服務？譬如在抗爭期間，因為黑警封路攔截車輛，而令求醫市民受到阻礙的病人，可否也向黑警提出民事索償？<br />\n<br />\n因為黨鐵無端停駛封站，影響前往醫院求診的病人，是否也能提出民事索償？<br />\n<br />\n做人要公道，你要告醫護，可以，反正良心不是每個人都有的，我們無法阻止；但不能大細超，過往造成阻礙的黑警黨鐵，你可不能一句包容諒解便算數。<br />\n<br />\n幾多人在抗爭運動期間被黑警濫暴毆打，爆眼爆頭，他們都希望向黑警提出申索，但從未見過姐姐葉劉伸個頭出來支援。<br />\n<br />\n那些無端受傷受影響的市民難道就不值得幫忙？<br />\n<br />\n我知道今天不是翻舊帳的時候，但有些事情對比實在太明顯。譬如強制隔離，明明用緊急法立例，要求內地入境的旅客和香港居民要家居隔離，偏偏違反禁令的人，勸喻警告再警告，卻沒有即時懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n我想起同樣都是用緊急法，都是先通過後審議的「禁蒙面法」，大家記得政府是如狼似虎，見人戴口罩便查便喝罵甚至拘捕，而且效率迅速，即捕即上庭。<br />\n<br />\n兩相對比，為何對違反隔離的人客客氣氣，對禁蒙面法的市民便要生要死？違反禁蒙面法不會害死人，但違反隔離檢疫的人，卻可以累街坊，四處播毒。<br />\n<br />\nOK我們明白的，這個政權只怕「港獨」卻不怕「病毒」，但大細超至此，實在不服氣。<br />\n<br />\n再看看警察全副武裝，生化危機，卻在事發現場十萬丈遠的距離，而醫護和病患零距離，卻又要重用自己的N95口罩，你還好意思要起訴醫護嗎？不如，先起訴拿了懲教署口罩再用警車送貨的人吧？ <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"7cdf602f95d5c8b1f84f967117cd94fd8996c7c1","tid":1876248,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T09:27:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">喺屋企家居隔離緊？<br />\n無口罩出唔到街？<br />\n喺街排緊隊買口罩？<br />\n咁快啲過嚟<span style=\"color: blue;\">Twitter</span>戰線！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要光復香港撳幾個掣都唔得？</span></span><br />\nTwitterHelpBot嘅tasklist 24小時更新<br />\n入去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GPcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=ab815985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">RT + Like + Comment</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">/task2 缺人！快啲入去幫手！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/quicktake/status/1227467414394331137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fquicktake%2Fstatus%2F1227467414394331137&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GPcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=936e0578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fquicktake%2Fstatus%2F1227467414394331137&h=6682e83f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/quicktake/status/1227467414394331137</a><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/IoWBobSeely/status/1227341171019730949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=